[Course_Description]
Get up and running quickly with Instagram, the popular photo-sharing social network. Staff instructor Garrick Chow begins by showing how to find and follow other users and topics of interest. Next, Garrick explains how to take and post your own pictures, shoot videos, and process your images using the many Instagram filters, as well as add captions and hashtags to your posts. He offers tips for building your network and developing a community of followers. Plus, learn how to build Instagram stories—a sequence of photos and videos that expire after a day—and message other users.